Ecuador ' s net reserves up to $ 1 . 87 bln at March 21 . Ecuador ' s Central Bank said Monday its net international reserves stood at $ 1 . 87 billion on March 21 , up $ 9 million from the week before . Reserves stood at $ 1 . 83 billion at the end of last year , up $ 274 million from the end of 1995 . ( ( - - Gustavo Oviedo , Quito Newsroom , 5932 258433 ) ) 
